OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773821069
OL,3,CStarmer tells Zelenskyy UK's focus
OL,4,C'must remain on Ukraine' despite Iran
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer told Volodymyr
OL,8,FZelenskyy that the UK's focus "must
OL,9,Fremain on Ukraine" despite the war in
OL,10,FIran, as he welcomed the president to
OL,11,FDowning Street.
OL,13,FWelcoming the Ukrainian president to
OL,14,FDowning Street, the Prime Minister
OL,15,Freiterated the UK's support for Kyiv,
OL,16,Fsaying: "Our resolve is unbreakable."
OL,18,FHe said: "I think it's really
OL,19,Fimportant that we are clear that the
OL,20,Ffocus must remain on Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773821069
OL,3,CStarmer tells Zelenskyy UK's focus
OL,4,C'must remain on Ukraine' despite Iran
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,F"There's obviously a conflict in Iran
OL,8,Fgoing on, in the Middle East, but we
OL,9,Fcan't lose focus on what's going on in
OL,10,FUkraine and the need for our support."
OL,12,FHe added: "Putin can't be the one who
OL,13,Fbenefits from a conflict in Iran,
OL,14,Fwhether that's oil prices or the
OL,15,Fdropping of sanctions."
OL,17,FZelenskyy thanked the UK for its
OL,18,Fsupport, adding: You have stood with
OL,19,Fus all through this difficult winter."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773821069
OL,3,CStarmer tells Zelenskyy UK's focus
OL,4,C'must remain on Ukraine' despite Iran
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FThe Ukrainian president said he would
OL,8,Fupdate Starmer on battlefield
OL,9,Fdevelopments and energy security,
OL,10,Fsaying: "Of course, we can't sleep, we
OL,11,Fmust move quickly."
OL,13,FHe said: "Also not to forget about our
OL,14,Fdiplomatic efforts and negotiations
OL,15,Fand where we are with the Americans
OL,16,Fand with the Russians."
OL,18,FZelenskyy also acknowledged the impact
OL,19,Fof the Iran war on Ukraine and Europe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
