PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773821069
OL,3,CStarmer tells Zelenskyy UK's focus
OL,4,C'must remain on Ukraine' despite Iran
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FThe King met Zelenskyy in Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace's first-floor drawing room
OL,9,Fbefore the president was invited to
OL,10,Ftake tea with the monarch in his
OL,11,Fprivate study during the 25-minute
OL,12,Fmeeting.
OL,14,FCharles and Zelenskyy greeted one
OL,15,Fanother with mutual warmth and
OL,16,Frespect, building on their many
OL,17,Fprevious encounters, the Press
OL,18,FAssociation understands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773821069
OL,3,CStarmer tells Zelenskyy UK's focus
OL,4,C'must remain on Ukraine' despite Iran
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FThe King, who in January paid tribute
OL,8,Fto the Ukrainian people's resilience
OL,9,Fand the country's "valiant strength",
OL,10,Fand expressed his hopes for a "just
OL,11,Fand lasting peace", is said to have
OL,12,Frearticulated these sentiments in
OL,13,Fperson to Mr Zelensky.
OL,15,FStarmer is expected to be among around
OL,16,F60 MPs and peers attending Zelenskyy's
OL,17,Fspeech.
OL,19,FDefence Secretary John Healey, leaders
OL,20,Fof the opposition parties and Nato
OL,21,Fchief Mark Rutte will also be present.
